  "title": "Reformer Pilates Instructor",
  "description": "<p>Jal Yoga International is a well-established wellness studio with six locations across Singapore, offering Yoga, Pilates, and Barre classes. With a growing presence in Malaysia, Indonesia, Dubai, and the Philippines, we are proud to be expanding our footprint in the region.</p><p>We are a passionate, dynamic, and fun-loving family, and we're looking for like-minded individuals to join us in our mission. If you’re passionate about the wellness industry and seeking an environment where you can learn, grow, and make a meaningful impact, this could be the perfect opportunity for you!</p><p>With the introduction of Reformer Pilates, we are seeking Part time instructors who can teach at our studio in East Coast.  We require the candidates to have the followings:</p><p>- Reformer Pilates Instructor Certification</p><p>- Minimum 1 year of fitness coaching experience </p><p>- Strong communication skills</p><p>- Passionate about helping people through reformer pilates</p>",
