    "uen": "201708359E",
    "description": "<p>JAL Yoga is a new yoga/pilates/barre&nbsp;concept studio started by people passionate about yoga practices. &nbsp;It has been very encouraging to see the increase in popularity of Yoga and we believe the market potential is still largely untapped in many parts of Singapore. &nbsp;At JAL, we believe yoga should be an integral part of one's health regimen regardless what kind of sports one engages in. &nbsp;Our mission is&nbsp;<strong>to inspire people to do what they think they cannot do with their minds and bodies so that they maintain good health to pursue their passion</strong>. &nbsp;As such, JAL will be introducing several new classes including 3 of those that we have patented for, to engage both beginners and regular practitioners. &nbsp;We are also the first in Singapore to introduce I<strong>nfrared Heat Yoga</strong> what makes practising hot yoga a lot more beneficial to health and complexion!<br>\nWe aim to create a lifestyle brand to engage a wider community to adopt healthy living in everything they do. &nbsp;Our vision is to build a sustainable organisation to help under-privilege in the society eventually.</p>",
